creator: SoFi Stadium and Hollywood Park
descriptionHtml:
Use the SoFi Stadium app to enhance your experience and stay connected to what’s happening at SoFi Stadium, YouTube Theater and Hollywood Park. Cheer on the Los Angeles Chargers and Los Angeles Rams and experience concerts, games and more live events.

- Experience all SoFi Stadium has to offer and discover upcoming events

- Access your event tickets and seat information

- Locate your parking lot and entry gate for navigation

- Check out our locally curated food and beverage options

- Explore and navigate points of interest throughout SoFi Stadium

- Find accessibility service locations

- Locate ride-sharing services
descriptionShort: Enhance your experience with mobile ticketing, stadium navigation and more!
